'''''findë''''' means "hair", or mor specifically "a tress or plait of hair", in [[Quenya]].<ref name=PM>{{PM|Shibboleth}}, pp. 345, 362</ref>

==Etymology==

The word derives from [[Common Eldarin]] ''[[phini-]]'' ("a single hair") and ''[[phindē]]'' ("a tress").<ref name=PM/>

